        "start": "03:14.000",
        "end": "03:17.500",
        "original": "今年も体力測定で力をつけてきたけど...",
        "english": "I've been building up my strength with fitness tests this year too, but...",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:17.500",
        "end": "03:20.500",
        "original": "みんな知ってる？なんでラミィがあんなに頑張ってたか。",
        "english": "Does everyone know? Why I was working so hard?",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:21.000",
        "end": "03:25.000",
        "original": "実はね、ヒーローになるためなんだー！",
        "english": "The truth is, it was all to become a hero!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
        "type": "dialogue"
      },
      {
        "start": "03:26.000",
        "end": "03:29.000",
        "original": "ドドーン！",
        "english": "Ta-da!",
        "alignment_source": "audio_tokens",
